  "texts": [
    "The review also compares a range of AI methods, including traditional machine learning, deep learning, and hybrid models, to help identify suitable approaches for different sensory tasks.",
    "Furthermore, it explores emerging trends such as multimodal fusion, interpretability, and ethical challenges, expanding the scope beyond conventional frameworks.",
    "By synthesizing recent progress and outlining key obstacles, this work defines the role of AI in advancing multisensory modeling and offers guidance for future interdisciplinary research.",
    "These insights support a comprehensive understanding of AI's impact on food innovation, health diagnostics, and environmental monitoring.",
    "The structure of this review is organized as follows: In Sect. 2, we provide an overview of the biological mechanisms underlying olfaction and gustation to enhance understanding of how these senses function."
